                  <!-- ********* <decoDesc> ********* -->
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote ana="#xx">
                        <ab>Inscription is two parts stretched across the upper part of the second mosaic 
                    band, a three-panel composition featuring the Torah shrine flanked by two menorot.
                    Inscription 2, I is in two lines above the lefthand menorah and inscription 2, II
                    is above the righthand menorah. The central portion of the text is missing; it
                    must have consisted of three lines symmetrically in the middle panel.</ab>
                        <locus/>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
